gw.api.domain

Interface RefersOutOfDomainGraph

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    APDPolicyInvolvedParty, BAPolicyContactRole, BOPPolicyContactRole, CPPolicyContactRole, GLPolicyContactRole, IMPolicyContactRole, PAPolicyContactRole, PlcyNonPriNamedInsured, PolicyAddlInsured, PolicyAddlInterest, PolicyAddlNamedInsured, PolicyAddress, PolicyBillingContact, PolicyContactRole, PolicyDriver, PolicyLaborClient, PolicyLaborContractor, PolicyLocation, PolicyNamedInsured, PolicyOwnerOfficer, PolicyPriNamedInsured, PolicySecNamedInsured, WCLaborContact, WCPolicyContactRole

    public interface RefersOutOfDomainGraph
    Delegate Interface for entities inside the Archiving Domain Graph that have a FK that points out of the EffDated graph. Implementors of this delegate should also add all instances to the implementation of IPolicyPeriodPlugin.getTrackedOutOfGraphReferences()

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.util.Map<ILinkPropertyInfo,KeyableBean> getReferencedBeans()
      Return a Map of ILinkPropertyInfos to the KeyableBeans outside the Archiving Domain Graph that the ILinkPropertyInfo points to.
      void recordExternalReferences()
      Records references out of the Archiving Domain Graph when the PolicyPeriod is locked.

    • Method Detail

      • recordExternalReferences

        void recordExternalReferences()
        Records references out of the Archiving Domain Graph when the PolicyPeriod is locked. This allows an opportunity to mark the referenced beans as needed.

      • getReferencedBeans

        java.util.Map<ILinkPropertyInfo,KeyableBean> getReferencedBeans()
        Return a Map of ILinkPropertyInfos to the KeyableBeans outside the Archiving Domain Graph that the ILinkPropertyInfo points to.
        Returns:
        Map of ILinkPropertyInfo -> KeyableBean that this EffDated refers to outside the Archiving Domain Graph
